jcuda.jcublas

Class cublasDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • jcuda.jcublas.cublasDataType

  • public class cublasDataType
extends java.lang.Object
    An enumerant to specify the data precision. It is used when the data reference does not carry the type itself (e.g void *)

    For example, it is used in the routine JCublas#cublasSgemmEx.
